# Challenges Faced

### Google OAuth Configuration

Managing OAuth scopes, consent screens, and API permissions required significant setup and debugging.

### Calendar Data Interpretation

Meeting titles are often vague, making project attribution difficult.

### AI Classification Accuracy

Balancing attribution confidence while minimizing incorrect project assignments was challenging.

### Cost Modeling

Creating realistic workforce cost calculations without accessing actual payroll systems required a flexible abstraction layer.

### Performance Optimization

Repeated AI calls increased latency and costs, leading to the implementation of classification caching.

